author: Paula Seftas
title: Paula Seftas
text: Best experience ever!!Couldn't find a particular dress anywhere in PA that my daughter was looking for. Wonderful sales girl helped me to order this dress. It came in perfectly packaged with quick delivery and actually cheaper than the same dress here in PA. Glad now I couldn't find the size!!
